body: "CodeFactor auto-issue GH-582 (2026-07-18, commit 6b8ee9e4 = PR#580 merge) flags src/cli/register-list-query.ts runRegisteredListCommand L181-241 as Complex Method. The method PASSES the repo twin gates (cyclomatic<=16 + sonarjs/cognitive-complexity<=16 enforced since pm-2gvp/GH-518) and holds NO entry in eslint-suppressions.json — CodeFactor's internal Complex-Method radar sits below our 16/16 policy threshold. Grade hygiene (pm-92if A+ goal) still wants it cleared: mechanically extract the status/brief/dependency-blocked option-assembly branches into named helpers; do NOT add a suppression (suppressions are the pm-j8vq grandfathered baseline, frozen for burn-down). Distinct from GH-583 (cli-bootstrap.ts), which IS suppression-backed and maps to pm-j8vq — never merge the two dispositions."
